import React from "react"; import jobliststyle from "./joblist.css"; const Joblist=({firstname,state,address,lastname,pnumber})=>{ return(

State: {state}

Address: {address}
FullName: {firstname +" "+ " "+lastname}
Phone Number: {pnumber}
) } export default Joblist;
